questions.quote: Okay. Umm, y'know, I don't think, I don't think I told you this, but umm, I just got out of a really serious relationship.
Ooh, then I guess the panty raid last night was totally uncalled for. Ok, I am going to take a shower and today I will be singing Jim Crochee's Leroy Brown.
Lewis Posin! He was my best friend in fifth grade, and-and then one day I asked him to be my boyfriend and he said no. Do you know why?
Okay, you said I could sing at your wedding so, I'm just gonna need a small deposit.
What 'not work out'? I'm seeing her again on Thursday. Didn't you listen to the story?
...and the style number, and the invoice number, and the shipping date. Good. Any questions so far?
That's nice... now, was that before or after you told him to stop calling, stop sending you flowers and to generally leave you alone, hmm?
I want you to tell her everything. About the deal you tried to make with me, about the crazy questions you... Wally Cox! That's the voice of Underdog!
No! No-no-no-no-no-no. It sounds like they really need you down there.
Wow, hey, we'd better get going. If we don't leave right now, we'll be late for dinner.
